snippet.title: C.H.A.S.E.D. Trailer
snippet.description:
You were quietly in your home when suddenly a Stranger starts stalking you, who knows what kind of wicked mind has, just stop him from getting inside! Is he the only one chasing you? and what kind of events and consequences will this unleash?

C.H.A.S.E.D. on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1077210/CHASED
Twitter : https://twitter.com/RoseHoodGames1
